    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This FD3S-generation RX-7 retains its iconic 13B-REW twin-rotor powerplant, featuring the sophisticated sequential twin-turbocharger system that delivers a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a front-mid engine configuration and a 50:50 weight distribution. Recent maintenance includes a full cooling system overhaul and vacuum line refreshment to ensure boost stability. Equipped with a five-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, this rotary icon offers an unfiltered analog driving experience. The exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, but the structural integrity and mechanical vitals remain robust.",
