    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in a stunning Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive mechanical shape. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the passenger-side rear bumper from a tight parking garage\u2014typical wear that does not detract from its overall curb appeal. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is smoke-free and remarkably clean; all power features, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and heated/ventilated seats, function exactly as they should. We have a complete folder of service records showing consistent oil changes every 5,000 miles and a comprehensive multi-point inspection performed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly without hesitation. This is an honest, well-cared-for luxury SUV that offers a perfect balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner.",
